properties.SQL select query: select top 10000000 u_name, age, company, birth_date from users;
select name as u_name, age, company, birth_date from users limit 10000000;

properties.Script Body:
%dw 2.0
output application/json deferred=true

  u_name: $.name,
  "age": $.age,
  "company": $.company,
  "birth_date": $.birth_date
}
